          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "High Volume Manual Inquiries and Operational Bottlenecks"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Their HR department was overwhelmed by a high volume of redundant, transactional questions regarding company policies. Traditional support methods were inefficient, forcing staff to rely on manual, reactive processes rather than scalable, real-time solutions."
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "FACING SIMILAR CHALLENGES?",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Key business areas impacted included:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "HR Productivity and Strategic Focus"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Employee Experience and Satisfaction"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Operational Scalability and Response Times"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Operational Scalability and Response Times"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "As a result, HR teams were consumed by repetitive tasks, leading to delayed responses and a lack of 24/7 self-service support for the organization."
        }
      ],
